<para style="p">A musical composition of David, which he sang to Yahweh concerning the words of Cush the Benjamite.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh my God, I take refuge in you!</para>

<para style="q1">Save me from all who chase me, and rescue me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Otherwise, they will rip me apart like a lion,</para>

<para style="q1">tearing me in pieces with no one else able to bring me to safety.</para>
